headline: Shelf-Stable Food Stocks Q2 Recap: Benchmarking Campbell's (NASDAQ:CPB)
summary: As the Q2 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the shelf-stable food industry, including Campbell's (NASDAQ:CPB) and its peers.
